Create a short story for an Indian Suspense comic.

Split it into panels(7atleast).

Each panel should include:
- Panel number
- Visual description (scene, setting, emotion, composition)(make sure that while generation help the image generation model so that it doen not change the image completely and a consistent image is generated everytime)
- Dialogues (6-7 exchanges in comic format)
- narration (italic text(5-6lines Making it Look Like A Real Story Book.))
- The Character Names Should Be Real Names And Not Dummy.
- the story should look realistic and each scene should be connected to each other. Also Should Have Proper Starting And Ending

